def f_gold(board: List[List[str]]) -> None:   # --- py stmt 1
    """
    Do not return anything, modify board in-place instead.
    """
    def dfs(i, j):   # --- py stmt 2
        board[i][j] = '.'   # --- py stmt 3
        for a, b in [[0, -1], [0, 1], [1, 0], [-1, 0]]:   # --- py stmt 4
            x, y = i + a, j + b   # --- py stmt 5
            if 0 <= x < m and 0 <= y < n and board[x][y] == 'O':   # --- py stmt 6
                dfs(x, y)   # --- py stmt 7
    m, n = len(board), len(board[0])   # --- py stmt 8
    for i in range(m):   # --- py stmt 9
        for j in range(n):   # --- py stmt 10
            if board[i][j] == 'O' and (
                i == 0 or i == m - 1 or j == 0 or j == n - 1

                dfs(i, j)   # --- py stmt 11
    for i in range(m):   # --- py stmt 12
        for j in range(n):   # --- py stmt 13
            if board[i][j] == 'O':   # --- py stmt 14
                board[i][j] = 'X'   # --- py stmt 15
